API 
websites are divided into frontend and backend
frontend is for user interface
Backend is used for storing data, for managing the data,
behind the scenes backend kaam karta hai , 
authentiation vegra user de sab user dekhta hai

server and clients both are computers
server pe backend wala application run hota hai
clients pe frontend wala application run hota hai

server is connected to database
frontend request send karta hai backend ko 
and backend response send karta hai frontend ko

API - application Programming Interface
backend ka 1 part API hai

jo bhi communication hote hai frontend and backend ke bech me to vo API ke through hote hai
API - Backend AND frontend

API me endPoints hote hai 
EndPoints are basically URL's
API means IS URL pe agr request bhejo ge to aapko ya wala data mile
